# Introduction 
This is how you can start being an ISV partner from Microsoft. Resources were highlighted throughout the years of 

Step 1: Create Microsoft Partner Network (MPN) Account – using SG entity[Please provide me MPN ID once received]
Step 2: Build-With Microsoft on Azure [ongoing with Chun, do provide me the Azure subscription ID once you have it]
Step 3: Publish solution in Azure Marketplace via Partner Center
Step 4: Achieve threshold of USD $100k for trailing 12 months net new Azure consumption – to be IP Co-sell ready
Step 5: Include Go-To-Market materials in “Co-Sell with Microsoft” Tab
Step 6: IP Technical Validation with Azure architecture reference diagram
Step 7: Share pipeline and close Co-Sell deals [we can jump start this process with existing deals]
